<section class="project-content">
  <div class="summary">
    <h2>Reducing plastic waste in the Amazon with design</h2>
    <p class="summary-text">designed a <a style="text-decoration: underline;" target=”_blank” href="https://3eeed6f4-f802-4461-9042-b0fbb17c7fc3.filesusr.com/ugd/0ec7ce_e36950ef1d5f434a9842db913aea108a.pdf">manual</a>  for indigenous Amazonian communities to upcycle plastic water bottles into useful tools, toys and raw materials, including ceiling lights, joints, games and jewelry</p>
  </div>
