<section class="problem">
  <h2>the problem ✍️</h2>
  <p>My team immersed ourselves in the indigenous community of Puerto Nariño, Colombia in partnership with local organizations Omacha and Natutama Foundation. Our task was to create a sustainable, social project to improve the daily life of the community. While we were conducting field research, we discovered both the strong manual skill and practices of this remote Amazon community and in our visit to the landfill, my team and I identified issues with the large amount of plastic that was inundating the forest. We decided to tackle this issue, by creating Replastic, rethinking plastic as not trash, but instead your next creation.</p>
</section>

